description: Viktor Babaryko was held amid pressure on opposition figures before August's presidential election.
title: Belarus: Rival of President Lukashenko arrested ahead of election
title_page: Belarus: Rival of President Lukashenko arrested ahead of election - BBC News
maintext: "Babaryko is detained because he was the organiser and leader of illegal activities, (and) tried to influence witness testimony," Ivan Tertel, the head of the state control committee, told the AFP news agency.
